    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm doing some research for a paper on foreign policy. can u help me out? i'm looking at the US involvement in the Libyan intervention back in 2011. from a strictly geopolitical and strategic standpoint, would you say that intervention was ultimately a success or a failure?",
